Cocktail generator for pi0, eta, omega, eta' production with real pt spectrum

Each meson has to be generated in a separate run. 
Meson PDG code and colliding system are set via environment variables
      CONFIG_MESON_PDG and CONFIG_BEAMS

Authors: D.Peressounko, B.Polushchuk, Y.Kharlov. 09-Jun-2012
